import{_ as e,o as t,c as r,b as o}from"./app-a6eacc5a.js";const a={},s=o('<h1 id="driver-software" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#driver-software" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Driver Software</h1><p>Driver software, or device drivers, are programs that enable communication between a computer&#39;s operating system and various hardware devices such as printers, keyboards, mice, monitors, sound cards, and more. They are responsible for translating the commands sent by the operating system into actions that can be understood by the specific device.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translatoion</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong><br> 驱动程序软件，或设备驱动程序，是能够在计算机操作系统和各种硬件设备(如打印机、键盘、鼠标、显示器、声卡等)之间进行通信的程序。它们负责将操作系统发送的命令转换为特定设备可以理解的操作。</p></details><p>Each type of hardware device requires its own driver to function properly on a computer. For example, a printer driver allows the computer to communicate with a printer and send print jobs to it, while a video card driver enables the computer to display graphics and videos on the monitor.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong><br> 每种硬件设备都需要自己的驱动程序才能在计算机上正常运行。例如，打印机驱动程序允许计算机与打印机通信并向其发送打印作业，而视频卡驱动程序则允许计算机在显示器上显示图形和视频。</p></details><p>Driver software is typically installed during the setup process when a new device is connected to a computer. It may also be downloaded and installed <code>manually</code> from the <code>manufacturer&#39;s</code> website. However, <code>outdated</code> or <code>corrupted</code> drivers can cause problems with device functionality and performance. Therefore, it is important to regularly update and maintain driver software to ensure <code>optimal</code> device performance and compatibility.</p><details class="custom-container details"><summary>translation</summary><p><strong>sentence:</strong><br> 当新设备连接到计算机时，驱动程序软件通常在设置过程中安装。 它也可以从制造商的网站手动下载和安装。 然而，过时或损坏的驱动程序可能会导致设备功能和性能问题。 因此，定期更新和维护驱动程序软件以确保最佳设备性能和兼容性非常重要。</p><p><strong>words:</strong><br> manually<br><code>英 [ˈmænjuəli]美 [ˈmænjuəli]</code></p><blockquote><p>adv. 手动地；用手</p></blockquote><p>manufacturer<br><code>英 [ˌmænjuˈfæktʃərə(r)]美 [ˌmænjuˈfæktʃərər]</code></p><blockquote><p>n. 生产商，制造商</p></blockquote><p>outdated<br><code>英 [ˌaʊtˈdeɪtɪd]美 [ˌaʊtˈdeɪtɪd]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 过时的，陈旧的<br> v. 使过时（outdate 的过去式和过去分词形式）</p></blockquote><p>corrupted ( corrupting, corrupted, corrupts )<br><code>英 [kəˈrʌptɪd]美 [kəˈrʌptɪd]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 腐败的；毁坏的；崩溃的<br> v. （使）腐败；（使）堕落（corrupt 的过去分词）</p></blockquote><p>optimal<br><code>英 [ˈɒptɪməl]美 [ˈɑːptɪməl]</code></p><blockquote><p>adj. 最佳的，最适的</p></blockquote></details>',7),c=[s];function n(d,i){return t(),r("div",null,c)}const l=e(a,[["render",n],["__file","13-driver-software.html.vue"]]);export{l as default};
